# AI Chatbot Development - HexSoftware Internship Project

An interactive, AI-powered web chatbot developed during my **AI Chatbot Development** internship at **HexSoftware**. 
This chatbot is designed to provide automated, smart responses, enhancing user engagement and streamline communication.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

You can interact with the live deployed chatbot here:
👉 **[Live Chatbot Link](https://cdn.botpress.cloud/webchat/v3.6/shareable.html?configUrl=https://files.bpcontent.cloud/2026/05/22/08/20260522085237-20IRKL0D.json)**

---

## ✨ Features

*   **Natural Language Understanding (NLU):** Interprets and processes user intents efficiently.
*   **Context-Aware Conversations:** Maintains dialogue flow for a seamless user experience.
*   **Web-Based Interface:** Fully responsive design accessible directly through the browser.
*   **Dynamic Configuration:** Loaded securely using JSON-based cloud configurations via Botpress.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack & Tools

*   **Platform:** [Botpress Cloud](https://botpress.com/)
*   **Configuration:** JSON Cloud Storage (`bpcontent.cloud`)
*   **Deployment:** Botpress Webchat v3.6 Shareable Interface

---

